    "Hayward served as an advisor to the organization in America from 1973 to 1976 and from 1982 to 1984.": [],
    "She then became the director from 1977 to 1982 and 1984 to 1986.": [],
    "In 1975, Hayward delivered the Matthews Lectures at Columbia, titled \u201cEarly Gothic Stained Glass from Abbot Suger through the Reign of Saint Louis,\u201d a series that remains unpublished.": [
